  "text": "The following section provides statistical description and analysis of the data. One survey question is presented to investigate each of the four domains of social quality. The sample questions used to investigate each of the four domains were chosen because each question has been identified as an valid and reliable indicator of one of the four domains by the ENISQ in 2004 [CITATION_1] .",
